    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹跳硬币的冒险</h2>《Flip Coin》是一款在多种环境中弹跳硬币前进的游戏。小心操控硬币到达目的地并通关游戏！<br><br><br><strong>直观的操作</strong><br>使用简单直观的操控来弹跳硬币到目标。即使是初学者也能轻松掌握的操作方式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/d9383879866447451e3fb2ea19a2ea97.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=162 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/951c7cc1483244e4432948da0a631923.poster.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/951c7cc1483244e4432948da0a631923.webm?t=1721224879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/951c7cc1483244e4432948da0a631923.mp4?t=1721224879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多样的关卡</strong><br>多个主题的关卡准备就绪，让您体验新的挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/5484f5b52f0320f6b85d05e116e42eab.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>成就感</strong><br>通关时的成就感是本游戏的一大亮点。完美通关每个关卡，感受自我的成长。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/c3891e48531f85b4061bcad230e65f60.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
